body:
“Join My Gay Emo Band” AU

This is a pretty dumb idea for an AU but I couldn’t help myself. They’re a dorky band with no name (cuz I can’t think of a name).

Cinnamon is in the bass, Bitey on guitar, Kinky on drums, and Buddy the lead singer, being a diva.

These kiddos belong to @dreamy-94 and @digeridoodler
